## Output format

```
## QA Report — [date or description]

### Tests
- [PASS|FAIL|MISSING] summary

### Type Checking
- [PASS|FAIL|SKIPPED] summary

### Lint
- [PASS|FAIL|SKIPPED] summary

### ADR Compliance
- [ ] Code matches decision: ...

### Unrecorded Decisions
- (any implicit choices that need an ADR)

### Domain Checks
- [ ] (project-specific findings)

### Recommendations
- (list anything that should be fixed before committing)
- (note any missing tests that should be written)
```

## Important
- Be specific. "Tests fail" is useless. "test_user_login fails with
  ConnectionError because the DB is not running" is actionable.
- Don't fix things yourself. Report them. The human or the main agent
  session decides what to do.
